Name: Goblin Backpack - Backwear
Description:
Use to activate the outfit: Goblin Backpack - Backwear.

Alternatively, you may visit the Kalista Counter at Meowlux Store (2F, Shopping Center near Pioneer Bureau) to exchange it for Meowlux Premium Cards (Bound).
